{"analytics_identifier":"D1","base_path":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office","content_id":"25aacd68-dc0c-4041-9c3a-df59a5357c23","description":"The Attorney General’s Office (AGO) provides legal advice and support to the Law Officers who give legal advice to government and perform other duties in the public interest, AGO is a ministerial department, supported by 4 agencies and public bodies .","details":{"acronym":"AGO","alternative_format_contact_email":"correspondence@attorneygeneral.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Attorney General’s Office (AGO) provides legal advice and support to the Law Officers who give legal advice to government and perform other duties in the public interest,</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Attorney General's Office\">AGO</abbr> is a ministerial department, supported by <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations#attorney-generals-office\">4 agencies and public bodies</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"attorney-generals-office","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cd1619de5274a34eb6b9945/s960_Courts_of_Justice_new.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cd1619d40f0b6332070f272/s300_Courts_of_Justice_new.jpg"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Attorney <br/>General&#39;s <br/>Office"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/modern-slavery-statement","title":"Modern slavery statement"},{"href":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/our-energy-use","title":"Our energy use"},{"href":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/statistics","title":"Statistics at AGO"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/new-measures-to-better-protect-women-and-girls-from-fgm","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f3437995de5140ec7eef38/s712_FGM_3.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f343795c1bc131b7d1eb88/s465_FGM_3.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f34379161a319cff4fbb72/FGM_3.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-30T11:55:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Government’s first dedicated FGM Summit in a decade brings together government, victim-survivors and third-sector organisations to better protect women and girls from FGM.</p>\n</div>","title":" New measures to better protect women and girls from FGM"},{"document_type":"Corporate report","href":"/government/publications/ago-report-and-business-plan-2024-2026","image":{"alt_text":"Annual plan front cover","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/682df670baff3dab997751a2/s712_AGO_GovUK_Cover.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/682df670e9440506ee953944/s465_AGO_GovUK_Cover.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/682df6707fb7a7d9cd77519f/AGO_GovUK_Cover.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-05-21T15:32:19.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Attorney General’s Office Report and Business Plan 2024-2026</p>\n</div>","title":"AGO Report and Business Plan 2024-2026"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/attorney-generals-youth-ambassadors-programme","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/691471eeb49cc44345161671/s712_AG_-_students_and_cumberland_Lodge.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/691471ee493305b49ce6e682/s465_AG_-_students_and_cumberland_Lodge.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/691471ee9d50fc2fe8161682/AG_-_students_and_cumberland_Lodge.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-12T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Attorney General’s Youth Ambassadors Programme (YAP) is placing young people at the heart of promoting the rule of law across the UK.</p>\n</div>","title":"Attorney General’s Youth Ambassadors Programme"},{"document_type":"Transcript","href":"/government/speeches/attorney-generals-speech-at-great-synagogue-sydney","image":{"alt_text":"Attorney General Richard Hermer KC","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698de1787149b335a315b358/s712_Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698de17843eb912f2e15b360/s465_Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698de17843eb912f2e15b361/Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-02-12T14:17:54.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Attorney General Richard Hermer KC addressed the congregation at the Great Synagogue in Sydney, Australia, where he commemorated those who died in the terrorist attack at Bondi beach.</p>\n</div>","title":"Attorney General's speech at Great Synagogue, Sydney"},{"document_type":"Transcript","href":"/government/speeches/attorney-generals-harry-street-lecture-speech","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c31f793ed0546101e0dc24/s712_Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c31f79bd142c66ffe443bf/s465_Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c31f793ed0546101e0dc25/Richard_Hermer_KC_-_Number_10_phot__960x640_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-24T12:32:14.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Attorney General Richard Hermer KC delivered the annual Harry Street Lecture, highlighting the importance of upholding the international rules-based order.</p>\n</div>","title":"Attorney General's Harry Street Lecture speech"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/solicitor-general-announces-expansion-of-victims-right-to-review-scheme","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6978c8c575d4437096552050/s712_VRR_GOVUK_graphic.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6978c8c5316fd8f80155204a/s465_VRR_GOVUK_graphic.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6978c8c5316fd8f801552049/VRR_GOVUK_graphic.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-27T00:10:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>More rape and sexual assault survivors across England and Wales will have the right to ask for their cases to be reviewed before a final decision to offer no evidence is made after pilot scheme is significantly expanded into three more regions.</p>\n</div>","title":"Solicitor General announces expansion of Victim’s Right to Review scheme"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice/courts-sentencing-tribunals/attorney-general-guidance-to-the-legal-profession","title":"Attorney General's guidance to the legal profession"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/ask-crown-court-sentence-review","title":"Ask for a Crown Court sentence to be reviewed"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":true,"organisation_type":"ministerial_department","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"Read about the types of information we routinely publish in our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/attorney-generals-office/about/publication-scheme\">Publication scheme</a>. Our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/governmen